      <title>印尼第一季度GDP增速超预期，创三季度最高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesias-q1-gdp-growth-beats-forecasts-highest-3-qtrs-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼统计局周一公布的数据显示，在大选支出的推动下，印尼第一季度经济同比增长5.11%，为三个季度以来最高，略快于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesias-q1-gdp-growth-beats-forecasts-highest-3-qtrs-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 04:21:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚第一季度 GDP 同比增速快于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-posts-quicker-than-expected-q1-gdp-growth-yryr-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼统计局周一公布的数据显示，第一季度印尼经济同比增长5.11%，快于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indonesia-posts-quicker-than-expected-q1-gdp-growth-yryr-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 04:16:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经合组织表示，新西兰联储必须保持政策限制，直到通胀低于目标</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rbnz-must-keep-policy-restrictive-until-inflation-falls-within-target-oecd-says-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经济合作与发展组织（OECD）周一表示，新西兰的货币政策必须保持限制性，直到通胀率控制在央行目标范围内，并敦促政府抑制支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rbnz-must-keep-policy-restrictive-until-inflation-falls-within-target-oecd-says-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:42:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国发现另外七家银行非法股票卖空</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-finds-illegal-stock-short-sales-by-seven-more-banks-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国市场监管机构周一表示，在对外国投资银行交易行为进行全面调查的过程中，发现国内股市又有七家银行违反卖空规定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/south-korea-finds-illegal-stock-short-sales-by-seven-more-banks-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:03:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜通过生日忠诚誓言支持领导人金正恩</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-bolsters-leader-kim-with-birthday-loyalty-oaths-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国一家研究机构表示，自领导人金正恩 2011 年掌权以来，朝鲜首次被要求在他生日那天宣誓效忠，同时该国还采取了其他措施来巩固他的统治。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-bolsters-leader-kim-with-birthday-loyalty-oaths-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:02:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾表示不会加剧南海紧张局势，不会使用高压水枪</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-wont-raise-south-china-sea-tensions-wont-use-water-cannons-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，该国不会在南海使用高压水枪或任何进攻性武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-wont-raise-south-china-sea-tensions-wont-use-water-cannons-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩联社报道，印度尼西亚提议削减韩国战斗机项目的付款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-proposes-cutting-payments-skorea-fighter-jet-project-yonhap-reports-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据韩国联合通讯社周一报道，印尼已提议将其在与韩国的联合战斗机研发项目中的付款份额削减至原先商定金额的三分之一左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-proposes-cutting-payments-skorea-fighter-jet-project-yonhap-reports-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:17:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储削减押注，亚洲股市上涨；日元回落涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场重新押注美联储今年可能会降息，亚洲股市周一上涨，而日元在上周因东京疑似货币干预而大幅上涨后走软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:14:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥当局确认失踪的美国、澳大利亚游客死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/mexican-authorities-confirm-missing-us-australian-tourists-have-died-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[下加利福尼亚州检察官办公室周日在一份声明中表示，上个月在墨西哥北部失踪的三名游客的家人已经辨认了他们的尸体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/mexican-authorities-confirm-missing-us-australian-tourists-have-died-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:04:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业报告疲软后美元持稳；日元本周开局不利</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-after-soft-us-jobs-report-yen-starts-week-back-foot-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元周一大体持稳，因疲软的美国就业报告提振了美联储今年仍可能降息两次的押注，而日元本周初小幅走软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-after-soft-us-jobs-report-yen-starts-week-back-foot-2024-05-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 01:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
